<!--
    IronCircle notification status bar icon.
    Must be: single colour, white, transparent background.
    The path is the IronCircle hexagon logo from splash.svg,
    with the two SVG transforms (translate + scale) pre-applied so
    the path coordinates sit inside the viewport naturally.

    Original transforms in splash.svg:
      translate(-157.129, -339.251)  then  scale(0.294834)
    Applied to bounding box of raw path:
      Raw X: 289.474 → 2233.81   →  after transform  →  X: 39.3 → 610.0
      Raw Y: 774.921 → 2990.59   →  after transform  →  Y: 128.7 → 542.0
    We use viewportWidth=650 viewportHeight=654 to give a square-ish viewport.

    Rather than re-computing every coordinate, we embed the path at its
    NATIVE coordinate space and set the viewport to that space directly.
    Android scales the whole thing to 24dp × 24dp automatically.
-->
<vector xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
    android:width="24dp"
    android:height="24dp"
    android:viewportWidth="1945"
    android:viewportHeight="2216">
